title: 27th Annual Cantor Louis Moss Memorial Concert
desc: It's time for the  27th Annual Cantor Louis Moss Memorial Concert , which will take place on the 7th night of Hanukkah,  Saturday December 12, 2015 at 7:30 pm . Join us for a celebratory evening with Hanukkah candle lighting, audience sing-alongs, and beautiful Jewish music Featuring: and featuring piano accompaniment by Shinae Kim General Admission tickets are $30 but  Early Bird $25 tickets  are available through  December 10 ! College and Graduate Students tickets are $10 (with valid ID) Children 18 and under are FREE (On-line ticket sales end 12/11 at 4:30pm. ?Tickets will also be available at the door.) Sponsorship opportunities are also available starting at $60!* Sign up now!
